Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.31,0:00:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fumizuki Academy is a new school that has\Nimplemented a special system for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.38,0:00:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, please begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.91,0:00:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first part of this system is the Exam Summoning Battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.33,0:00:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Battles are waged between\NSummoned Beings of different classes,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.62,0:00:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which are given form by the latest technology.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.68,0:00:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other key element of the system is classroom\Nfacilities which directly correspond to one's ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.58,0:00:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Students take a placement exam at the end of each school year,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.97,0:00:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and are then divided into six classes\Nfrom A through F based on their scores.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.18,0:00:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally time to take the placement exam...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.14,0:00:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This ain't gonna be a walk in the park, but I can handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.79,0:01:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Himeji!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.66,0:01:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay? Pull yourself together!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.52,0:01:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leaving the room during the exam will result in a zero. Am I clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.34,0:01:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But teach!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.55,0:01:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Yoshii?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.93,0:01:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.04,0:01:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshii...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.14,0:01:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're late, Yoshii.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.52,0:01:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ironman...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.65,0:01:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Mr. Nishimura, not Ironman.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.58,0:01:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go. You're the last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.79,0:01:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are the results of your placement exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.61,0:01:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be assigned to whatever class is written in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.27,0:01:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.51,0:01:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I might as well tell you this now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.80,0:01:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After everything you showed me last year, I had my suspicions that you were an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.91,0:01:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, after I saw your score, I realized that I was mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.77,0:02:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to apologize for doubting you, Yoshii. You're not an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.04,0:02:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're one hell of an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.59,0:02:24.02,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HF1DEEB&}Just who are we letting grow up on their own?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.83,0:02:25.05,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\an8\c&H9BBAFF&}One more chance! One more chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.14,0:02:26.37,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\an8\c&H9BBAFF&}Never, never give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.44,0:02:27.70,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\an8\c&HFFC7C4&}One more chance! One more chance!
