Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.69,0:03:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Fumizuki Academy is a new school that has\Nimplemented a special system for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.44,0:03:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell? Class F?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.13,0:03:59.81,Name Cards,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(645,56)}Akihisa Yoshii
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.26,0:03:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the worst class.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.05,0:03:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I thought I was gonna do well, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.55,0:03:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I have to have at least gotten 10% right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.60,0:04:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fumizuki Academy is a new school that takes pride in the fact that it uses only the latest study materials.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.40,0:04:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.27,0:04:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,System desks and reclining seats!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.40,0:04:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They even have laptops!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.02,0:04:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dear lord, a self-serving bar! Class A\Ncan have snacks whenever they want!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.90,0:04:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw floors... Floor cushions... Coffee tables...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.60,0:04:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my classroom!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.92,0:04:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reality is a harsh mistress at Fumizuki Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.43,0:04:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If one wishes to have a more comfortable educational experience, he or she must make better grades.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.45,0:04:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the academy's central tenet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.18,0:04:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God damn... So I guess this is a caste system, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.35,0:04:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshii, hurry up and sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.46,0:04:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. Where do I sit?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.81,0:04:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wherever you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.24,0:04:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no seating chart!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.51,0:04:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, my cushion doesn't have any stuffing in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.41,0:05:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just deal with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.56,0:05:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, but there's wind blowing in from the crack in the window. It's quite chilly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.55,0:05:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just deal with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.04,0:05:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, my table broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.96,0:05:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just deal with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.94,0:05:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.47,0:05:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.09,0:05:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, reality is truly cruel at Fumizuki Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.56,0:05:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Fukuhara, the teacher for this class.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.07,0:05:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope we'll have a-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.76,0:05:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go get this fixed. You\Ncan study whatever in the meantime.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.09,0:05:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, this place sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.53,0:05:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're supposed to spend the entire year here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.87,0:05:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, man, you shoulda scored better on the test if you were gonna bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.74,0:05:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuji! You're in this class too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.87,0:05:46.46,Name Cards,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(1065,581)}Sakamoto
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.99,0:05:46.46,Name Cards,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(1065,129)}Yuuji
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.23,0:05:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look who else is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.37,0:05:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo! Looks like I'm stuck here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.37,0:05:49.96,Name Cards,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an6\pos(207,586)}Shimada
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.50,0:05:49.96,Name Cards,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an6\pos(207,133)}Minami
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.96,0:05:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shimada!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.32,0:05:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm not surprised you're in F.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.55,0:05:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you calling me an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.59,0:06:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Owowowowow! This shit hurts when chicks without any tits do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.94,0:06:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nearly there...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.10,0:06:11.61,Name Cards,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(645,52)}Kouta Tsychiya
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.61,0:06:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't lived in Japan for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.26,0:06:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I couldn't read the questions, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.28,0:06:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it's pretty lively in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.23,0:06:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hideyoshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.24,0:06:22.12,Name Cards,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(1065,590)}Kinoshita
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.36,0:06:22.12,Name Cards,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(1065,133)}Hideyoshi
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.40,0:06:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in this class too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.08,0:06:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hopefully this won't suck too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.40,0:06:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can drink to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.70,0:06:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, yeah, this is the worst class in the entire school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.50,0:06:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of the guys in here look retarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.83,0:06:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That includes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.74,0:06:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness we have a cute girl like Hideyoshi!
