Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.51,0:06:40.05,Female Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(203,516)}Female
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.47,0:06:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.03,0:06:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Girls are beings who are so gentle and\Nkind that they can mend a broken heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.61,0:06:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shimada, on the other hand,\Nis rough, frightening, and flat...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.89,0:06:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jesus Christ, my spine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.06,0:06:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.40,0:06:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, I'm sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.99,0:07:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was in the nurse's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.11,0:07:03.41,Name Cards,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an6\pos(207,586)}Himeji
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.24,0:07:03.41,Name Cards,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an6\pos(207,133)}Mizuki
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.41,0:07:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Himeji...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.50,0:07:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshii!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.33,0:07:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshii!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.70,0:07:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.64,0:07:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't that hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.49,0:07:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna snap my spine into two!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.01,0:07:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna break... You bitch...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.01,0:07:25.73,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Nearly there...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.84,0:07:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't leave us, Voyeur!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.16,0:07:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Li... Li...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.38,0:07:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk! I'll call an ambulance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.70,0:07:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.61,0:07:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Voyeur!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.03,0:07:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, at least I'm not the only girl here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.56,0:07:50.52,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Voyeur! I'll save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.39,0:07:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no seating chart, so sit wherever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.52,0:07:53.71,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Save him! Somebody save him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.61,0:07:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.71,0:07:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, is that seat free?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.39,0:07:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.45,0:08:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you got placed into class F...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.97,0:08:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's make the best of it-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.43,0:08:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.43,0:08:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.39,0:08:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place is worn out as hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.31,0:08:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like, the cushions might as well be rocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.09,0:08:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The floor's a veritable breeding ground for mold.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.62,0:08:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't somewhere a sick person should be!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.08,0:08:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.62,0:08:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.35,0:08:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't school, like, a microcosm of society?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.77,0:08:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare they segregate us like this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.74,0:08:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they'll treat us like dogs if we complain about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.79,0:08:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As such, we'll simply have to challenge them fair and square.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.53,0:08:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once we come into power and gain the right to speak up, we'll tell the world about-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.79,0:08:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, you want somewhere more amenable to Himeji, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.14,0:08:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, come on! I was trying to make it sound all noble!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.22,0:08:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you have to ruin it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.56,0:09:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I was thinking the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.85,0:09:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.57,0:09:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to prove to the world that grades aren't everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.07,0:09:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty confident, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.73,0:09:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna try it, Akihisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.60,0:09:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, let's try out an Exam Summoning Battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.12,0:09:17.67,Sign Whatever,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\fnGaramond\fs60\pos(642,450)\be1\3c&H955534&\fad(200,0)}Exam Summoning Battle
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.63,0:09:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.22,0:09:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to propose something as your class representative.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.35,0:09:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want us to engage in an Exam Summoning Battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.55,0:09:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.75,0:09:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An Exam Summoning Battle? What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.40,0:09:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fumizuki Academy has a system called the Exam Summoning Battle, also known as the ESB.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.19,0:09:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Under the supervision of a teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.16,0:09:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,students can summon a Being with attack power proportional to their grades in a given subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.84,0:09:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They can challenge other classes using these Beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.47,0:09:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If a lower level class defeats a higher level\None, they will swap facilities and classrooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.74,0:09:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys, are you happy with this crappy room?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.66,0:09:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hell no!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.08,0:09:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we win an ESB,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.00,0:10:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll be able to get class A's fabulous room!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.92,0:10:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the lowest class.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.50,0:10:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bottom of this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.15,0:10:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're nothing but a bunch of garbage!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.70,0:10:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that means that we have nothing to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.77,0:10:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why don't we give it a shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.34,0:10:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we have him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.70,0:10:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshii Akihisa is a legendary Punishment Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.44,0:10:28.61,Sign Whatever,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp5\fs80\fnChubby Cheeks\pos(643,530)\c&H040A22&\3c&H262F79&\fad(200,0)}PUNISHMENT INSPECTOR
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.45,0:10:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.04,0:10:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! I've never seen one before!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.78,0:10:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! He's left me in despair!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.87,0:10:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, uh, not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.29,0:10:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Himeji?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.83,0:10:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are Punishment Inspectors strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.49,0:10:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Only very special people can be one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.10,0:10:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a title given to mentally\Ndisabled kids who get bad grades.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.60,0:10:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It translates to "Idiot".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.67,0:10:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, a worthless piece of crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.16,0:10:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.90,0:10:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just take me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.47,0:11:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we win an ESB, we can kiss this classroom goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.67,0:11:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What say we give it a try?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.98,0:11:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to start with the class directly above us - class E.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.29,0:11:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akihisa, you're now class F's ambassador.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.55,0:11:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go and declare war on class E.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.92,0:11:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.92,0:11:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bad things happen to ambassadors from weaker countries when they declare war?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.33,0:11:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, only in movies and novels.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.18,0:11:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, who on Earth would mess with an ambassador?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.96,0:11:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.92,0:11:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akihisa, you're the only one who can do this for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.28,0:11:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretend that I tricked you or something. Hop to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.35,0:11:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You tricked me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.81,0:11:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, this is about what I thought would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.98,0:11:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You predicted this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.39,0:11:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duh. I'm the rep for a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.90,0:11:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least act like you're sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.61,0:11:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can no longer turn back, Akihisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.82,0:11:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you prepared?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.98,0:11:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this what you wanted?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.63,0:11:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Don't worry, I'm ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.36,0:12:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? The sophomores have declared an ESB during the first semester?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.59,0:12:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.95,0:12:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have my permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.04,0:12:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.85,0:12:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put on a nice show for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.26,0:12:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our supervisor is Mr. Hasegawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.52,0:12:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seize him right before fifth period, while he's walking to class E.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.04,0:12:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hasegawa, the math teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.20,0:12:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Math is my thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.19,0:12:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Shimada will be our\Nmainline, since she's good at math.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.02,0:12:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Himeji, are you good at math?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.86,0:12:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.97,0:12:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then team up with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.39,0:12:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.94,0:12:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.07,0:12:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your attack points are equal to the\Ngrade you received on your last test.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.33,0:12:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our last test was...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.87,0:12:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The placement exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.04,0:12:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had to leave during the exam, so I got a 0.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.64,0:12:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can take a recovery exam once the ESB begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.30,0:13:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Himeji takes it, she'll be able to join us when she finishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.39,0:13:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.25,0:13:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.50,0:13:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.07,0:13:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've seized Mr. Hasegawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.49,0:13:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for war, people! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.16,0:13:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For crying out loud... these guys are friggin' morons.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.23,0:13:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys, it's time to sortie.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.93,0:13:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go teach those failures a lesson!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.72,0:13:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minami Shimada, reporting in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.79,0:13:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hideyoshi Kinoshita, ready to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.25,0:13:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kouta Tsychiya, same here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.79,0:13:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Permitted.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.15,0:13:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summoning Being!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.29,0:13:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.28,0:14:01.07,Summons,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(121,94)}Name:
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.37,0:14:01.07,Summons,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(901,94)}Subject:          {\fs40\c&H14FFF8&\3c&H9E636F&}Math
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.45,0:14:01.07,Summons,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(898,505)}Points:
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.13,0:14:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.70,0:14:06.50,Summons,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(121,94)}Name:
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.79,0:14:06.50,Summons,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(901,94)}Subject:          {\fs40\c&H14FFF8&\3c&H9E636F&}Math
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.87,0:14:06.50,Summons,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(898,505)}Points:
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.64,0:14:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.56,0:14:27.64,Summons,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(121,94)}Name:
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.64,0:14:27.64,Summons,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(850,109)}Subject:          {\fs40\c&H14FFF8&\3c&H9E636F&}Math
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.72,0:14:27.64,Summons,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(874,541)}Points:
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.64,0:14:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why was I the only one with a transformation sequence?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.29,0:14:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here they come.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.89,0:14:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful. Living flesh can't cross that barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.07,0:14:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wanna get past here, you're gonna have to beat us first.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.46,0:14:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshiko Mika, I accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.47,0:14:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.00,0:14:47.70,Summons,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(121,94)}Name:
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.08,0:14:47.70,Summons,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(901,94)}Subject:          {\fs40\c&H14FFF8&\3c&H9E636F&}Math
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.16,0:14:47.70,Summons,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(898,505)}Points:
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.94,0:14:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.06,0:14:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.21,0:14:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my line!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.31,0:14:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.40,0:14:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way class E can beat me at math!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.00,0:15:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who were KIA, meet in the detention room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.18,0:15:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.07,0:15:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ironman!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.09,0:15:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Acording to ESB rules, those whose points reach zero must receive supplementary lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.71,0:15:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Save me! I don't want to have detention with this monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.06,0:15:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to pass, then you have to defeat us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.27,0:15:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.78,0:15:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.16,0:15:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.83,0:15:27.74,Sign Whatever,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp5\be1\fs60\bord0\fnSansThirteenBlack\c&H706269&\pos(655,367)}Supply Room
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.74,0:15:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,

Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.75,0:15:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.50,0:15:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's our plan, Yuuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.04,0:15:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.98,0:15:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like tug-of-war - whichever class gets\Npushed back will have their classroom invaded.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.83,0:15:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if their rep gets defeated, that side loses.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.50,0:15:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That won't happen to us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.87,0:15:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! They're pushing us back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.07,0:15:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Class E has better grades overall.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.88,0:15:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we go head to head, it's only a matter of time before we lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.72,0:15:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.56,0:16:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, they are only class E. It'll take them a while to make it all the way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.05,0:16:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the time it'll take them to do that is the key to our victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.42,0:16:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My points...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.49,0:16:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're gonna murder us at this rate!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.22,0:16:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on standby and recover your points.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.84,0:16:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.18,0:16:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to take the recovery test!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.28,0:16:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever you recieve on this test will become your Being's attack points the next time you summon it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.26,0:16:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you score low, then your Being will become weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.32,0:16:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.40,0:16:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.75,0:16:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which subject?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.32,0:16:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Math, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.07,0:16:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to answer as much as I can to recover my points...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.85,0:16:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.17,0:16:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Voyeur!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.46,0:16:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.72,0:16:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.01,0:17:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.81,0:17:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Assault them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.61,0:17:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our defensive line is down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.27,0:17:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad, Yuuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.93,0:17:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Numbers are just numbers... they're not Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.53,0:17:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh god, kanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.91,0:17:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll skip this question.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.71,0:17:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who were KIA, meet in the detention room!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.63,0:17:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do, Yuuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.07,0:17:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you guys finished?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.09,0:17:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but it looks like it's about time for us to end this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.05,0:17:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, my, coming here yourself, eh? Don't underestimate us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.18,0:17:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you guys idiots? You declared an ESB as soon as school began.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.81,0:18:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just finished taking the placement exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.76,0:18:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our differences in class are equivalent to our differences in points.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.72,0:18:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you really think you'd win?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.17,0:18:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.86,0:18:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.79,0:18:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are in class F because you're so stupid, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.86,0:18:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuji, we're not going to be able to beat the classes above us without a plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.08,0:18:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, I do have a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.33,0:18:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Know why I kept you with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.85,0:18:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.16,0:18:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.76,0:18:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct! He's Akihisa Yoshii, the Punishment Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.47,0:18:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akihisa, show them your true power!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.85,0:18:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I've got no choice... It always comes down to me in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.36,0:18:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.79,0:18:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Punishment Inspector's Being has special powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.58,0:18:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it has to assist teachers with their chores as punishment,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.84,0:18:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's corporeal, unlike the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.43,0:19:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, any pain it feels will be felt by its summoner as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.83,0:19:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.62,0:19:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.93,0:19:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.72,0:19:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take care of that small fry first.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.39,0:19:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.34,0:19:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't take me down that easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.39,0:19:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.73,0:19:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Owowowowowow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.93,0:19:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It makes sense that you're the rep for E class.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.07,0:19:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your bodyguard's pretty damn useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.32,0:19:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, he's good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.02,0:19:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll finish you off personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.75,0:19:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.04,0:19:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Hiromi Nakabayashi, challenge you, Yuuji Sakamoto, to-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.30,0:19:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.73,0:19:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mizuki Himeji, I accept!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.92,0:19:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summoning Being.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.56,0:19:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.77,0:19:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.43,0:20:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are her points so high!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.11,0:20:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is class A level!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.96,0:20:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is a student like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.02,0:20:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.48,0:20:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Himeji!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.55,0:20:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mizuki Himeji... Don't tell me... you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.65,0:20:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshii!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.61,0:20:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinada?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.62,0:20:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's totally awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.75,0:20:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder she was a candidate for class A...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.75,0:20:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Himeji's score?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.92,0:20:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In Fumizuki Academy, you can take as many tests as you wish during the testing period.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.57,0:20:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As such, you can acquire as points as you are capable of.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.65,0:20:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, your plan was...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.67,0:20:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to buy time while she took the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.74,0:20:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one told me she was in class F!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.68,0:20:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.96,0:20:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.80,0:20:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Exam Summoning Battle ends in class F's victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.41,0:21:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you're amazing, Himeji!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.11,0:21:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.50,0:21:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're just saying that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.04,0:21:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we can switch classrooms and facilities with class E!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.92,0:21:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's better, at least...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.71,0:21:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, we're not switching facilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.30,0:21:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll keep what we have now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.52,0:21:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't you think it's a good idea, Nakabayashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.93,0:21:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.39,0:21:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, Yuuji? I mean, we won!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.56,0:21:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's over?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.48,0:21:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hideyoshi, why are you dressed like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.07,0:21:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh, that's it. You've finally understood the calling in your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.11,0:21:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm over here, Akihisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.05,0:21:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are two of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.69,0:21:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.36,0:21:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hideyoshi is my twin brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.21,0:21:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the ambassador from class 2A, Yuuko Kinoshita.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.36,0:21:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We, class A, declare war on you, class F.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.84,0:21:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is class A declaring war on us!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.59,0:21:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think we'll go easy on you just because you're the lowest class.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.45,0:22:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to obliterate you.
Comment: 0,0:22:04.85,0:22:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ending Keyframe
Dialogue: 1,0:22:18.72,0:22:21.67,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\c&HC45007&}It's a time of peace now that school's out.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:21.77,0:22:24.70,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\c&HC45007&}If I were to describe her, she's a real angel!
Dialogue: 1,0:22:24.86,0:22:27.70,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\c&H9100FE&}Then came a notice that shattered my fun.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:27.84,0:22:30.48,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\c&H9100FE&}It said I had to stay afterschool! It's like hell!!
Dialogue: 1,0:22:30.89,0:22:33.75,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\c&H0FF606&}I was talking about it with my friends, and I said,
Dialogue: 1,0:22:33.90,0:22:36.75,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\c&H0FF606&}"No way anyone's that stupid!!"
Dialogue: 1,0:22:36.95,0:22:39.87,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\c&H0000BC&}But deep inside me,
Dialogue: 1,0:22:40.00,0:22:42.37,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\c&H0000BC&}I was shouting out,
Dialogue: 1,0:22:42.58,0:22:44.12,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\c&H0000BC&}"I AM THAT STUPID!"
Dialogue: 1,0:22:44.68,0:22:47.25,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\3c&H3300AE&\c&H000000&}That sign in the parking lot
Dialogue: 1,0:22:47.71,0:22:50.46,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\3c&H3300AE&\c&H000000&}that says "Monthly"...{or "Tsukigime"}
Dialogue: 1,0:22:50.82,0:22:55.95,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\3c&H3300AE&\c&H000000&}I always thought that was the company's name.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:56.14,0:22:58.60,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ALWAYS.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:59.58,0:23:02.31,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\c&HA23500&}Stupidity's a character! A real man!
Dialogue: 1,0:23:02.59,0:23:05.24,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\c&HA23500&}Our common sense is the lack thereof!
Dialogue: 1,0:23:05.63,0:23:08.28,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\c&H1F009B&}We don't need rules in our fucking world!
Dialogue: 1,0:23:08.64,0:23:11.33,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\c&H1F009B&}Eat steak out every night, overthrow the mass!
Dialogue: 1,0:23:11.73,0:23:17.75,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\c&H99A000&}Take a look, the sun that rose from the west is setting back down!
Dialogue: 1,0:23:17.75,0:23:20.81,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\c&H99A000&}Run home, it's almost dinner!
Dialogue: 1,0:23:20.81,0:23:23.47,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\c&H99A000&}Let's get home!
Dialogue: 1,0:23:23.84,0:23:27.53,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\c&H99A000&}Let's get home!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.73,0:23:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Question 2:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.85,0:23:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please answer the following question:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.03,0:23:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This plant has roots which can be eaten. In English, it is known as a "lily".
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.89,0:23:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yam! Potato! Sweet potato!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.28,0:23:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please also pay attention to the second part of the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.74,0:23:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: Lilies and Roses and PE.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.78,0:23:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will be on your test.